Oh, she doesn't know.

01:19:43.120 --> 01:19:47.723
Oh, Red's my husband,
well fiance back then.

01:19:49.262 --> 01:19:52.529
It was a stupid, impulsive thing

01:19:52.530 --> 01:19:54.886
and it only happened once

01:19:54.887 --> 01:19:57.237
but we ended up with this
beautiful boy, Simon.

01:19:59.140 --> 01:20:00.939
Red knows now.

01:20:00.940 --> 01:20:02.679
It wasn't the cleanest of situations

01:20:02.680 --> 01:20:04.180
but most of that is behind us.

01:20:08.327 --> 01:20:09.970
I know it's a big thing Gwen.

01:20:11.100 --> 01:20:12.903
Simon is a part of my life.

01:20:14.850 --> 01:20:15.827
I come here every Sunday now

01:20:15.828 --> 01:20:18.160
and I imagine as he gets older,

01:20:18.161 --> 01:20:21.453
I'll want to come and see him more often.

01:20:23.210 --> 01:20:26.460
I don't expect you to be too
involved or anything but...

01:20:29.950 --> 01:20:31.900
I'd better go fill up Simon's bottle.

01:20:40.580 --> 01:20:41.413
Gwen.

01:20:42.311 --> 01:20:44.123
Just say something, please?

01:20:49.999 --> 01:20:54.019
It's fine.

01:20:54.020 --> 01:20:56.893
Joe, I can handle this.

01:20:58.780 --> 01:21:02.469
To be honest, it's not like I ever thought

01:21:02.470 --> 01:21:05.623
about having anything even
remotely close to a family.

01:21:06.520 --> 01:21:08.220
Any kind of attachment at all, but

01:21:10.870 --> 01:21:15.013
it feels kind of nice, to be
a part of something like this.

01:21:17.400 --> 01:21:18.233
I mean,

01:21:20.063 --> 01:21:20.896
I love you.

01:21:22.350 --> 01:21:25.016
Whoever thought I'd say
those words to anyone?

01:21:25.017 --> 01:21:26.803
And you obviously love Simon.

01:21:28.190 --> 01:21:29.209
There's no part of me that would want

01:21:29.210 --> 01:21:31.580
to take away either of those things.

01:21:37.253 --> 01:21:40.529
Hi Joe.

01:21:40.530 --> 01:21:43.069
Oh, hey Red.

01:21:43.070 --> 01:21:45.026
So you finally brought
your girlfriend over?

01:21:45.027 --> 01:21:45.860
Yeah.

01:21:47.527 --> 01:21:51.749
I've seen you before.
What?

01:21:51.750 --> 01:21:54.373
Last week, you were in
the car down the road.

01:22:04.300 --> 01:22:06.753
Gwen, what were you
doing here last week?

01:22:09.790 --> 01:22:12.413
Gwen?

01:22:29.052 --> 01:22:30.885
Gwen, what's going on?

01:22:32.933 --> 01:22:34.593
Have you been spying on me?

01:22:37.143 --> 01:22:39.343
Answer me, Gwen, what
the hell is going on?

01:22:43.440 --> 01:22:44.653
You were spying on me?

01:22:52.910 --> 01:22:54.210
Was it just this one time?

01:23:04.240 --> 01:23:05.820
Try to understand.

01:23:15.560 --> 01:23:17.000
Why did you do it?

01:23:19.413 --> 01:23:20.343
I told you.

01:23:22.223 --> 01:23:23.757
It was just curiosity.

01:23:27.570 --> 01:23:29.359
I just wanted to study you.

01:23:29.360 --> 01:23:31.560
I didn't plan the way
things ended up being.

01:23:34.070 --> 01:23:36.650
And you've done this
with what, 35 other people?

01:23:38.163 --> 01:23:40.135
Studied them, yeah.

01:23:40.136 --> 01:23:43.246
But you are the first one I even spoke to,

01:23:43.247 --> 01:23:45.080
more than momentarily.

01:23:47.480 --> 01:23:49.953
I'm trying, I'm trying to understand...

01:23:49.954 --> 01:23:52.537
You don't have to understand.

01:23:55.176 --> 01:23:57.783
You used me.
I didn't use you.

01:23:58.650 --> 01:24:00.959
I meant nearly everything I said.

01:24:00.960 --> 01:24:02.889
I just didn't tell you
about this one thing.

01:24:02.890 --> 01:24:05.169
What about all that other stuff, huh?

01:24:05.170 --> 01:24:08.459
All that other stuff we
coincidentially had in common?

01:24:08.460 --> 01:24:09.293
What about that?

01:24:10.570 --> 01:24:12.429
That was all bullshit.

01:24:12.430 --> 01:24:15.153
All written down in your
little book before we even met.

01:24:17.790 --> 01:24:19.269
Do you have any idea how hard it was

01:24:19.270 --> 01:24:20.669
for me to show you Simon?

01:24:20.670 --> 01:24:22.689
I told you it didn't need to be.

01:24:22.690 --> 01:24:24.197
Yeah, I guess not.

01:24:25.180 --> 01:24:27.229
You already knew about him.
I just,

01:24:27.230 --> 01:24:30.069
I wanted to know where
you went every Sunday.

01:24:30.070 --> 01:24:32.220
I hadn't followed you
in more than a month.

01:24:33.650 --> 01:24:35.699
I just, I didn't want you keeping

01:24:35.700 --> 01:24:37.643
that part of your life secret from me.

01:24:38.580 --> 01:24:39.513
And I didn't!

01:24:40.440 --> 01:24:42.749
I always was gonna tell you.

01:24:42.750 --> 01:24:44.679
But you didn't let me.

01:24:44.680 --> 01:24:46.299
You took that from me

01:24:46.300 --> 01:24:47.339
and it wasn't even yours to take

01:24:47.340 --> 01:24:48.240
but not just that,

01:24:50.430 --> 01:24:51.729
when I took you to the the lake

01:24:51.730 --> 01:24:54.180
to show you where I went
camping as a little boy,

01:24:55.370 --> 01:24:56.670
you already knew about it.

01:24:57.862 --> 01:25:01.387
When I showed you my portraits,
you'd already seen them.

01:25:04.075 --> 01:25:06.649
I was showing you some of
the most precious things

01:25:06.650 --> 01:25:07.663
in my life, I was,

01:25:09.051 --> 01:25:11.289
I was letting you in.

01:25:11.290 --> 01:25:14.093
I was letting you see
what was important to me.

01:25:16.530 --> 01:25:18.633
I thought I was showing
you something special.

01:25:23.160 --> 01:25:26.660
But you already fuckin' knew about it all.

01:25:36.650 --> 01:25:37.483
I think,

01:25:40.143 --> 01:25:42.823
I think I'm gonna need some
time to think about this Gwen.

01:25:45.040 --> 01:25:45.873
It's just

01:25:49.018 --> 01:25:49.851
so...

01:27:03.712 --> 01:27:05.819
Are you coming to bed Joe?

01:27:05.820 --> 01:27:06.670
It's pretty late.

01:27:09.200 --> 01:27:10.033
In a minute.

01:27:13.770 --> 01:27:15.360
Do you want to talk about it?

01:27:15.361 --> 01:27:19.743
No, I just need some time alone.

01:28:45.715 --> 01:28:46.548
Sorry.

01:29:24.961 --> 01:29:25.961
Hey.
Hey.

01:29:29.150 --> 01:29:31.150
I'm sorry about all that stuff before.

01:29:33.320 --> 01:29:34.163
Do you think,

01:29:35.510 --> 01:29:37.910
maybe now you've had a
chance to think about it,

01:29:40.100 --> 01:29:41.083
there's any way?

01:29:42.450 --> 01:29:43.283
Gwen.

01:29:45.570 --> 01:29:46.570
You're a sweet girl.

01:29:48.360 --> 01:29:50.260
There's a lot I really like about you.

01:29:51.500 --> 01:29:55.863
But, I just don't think
we can go on after this.

01:29:57.726 --> 01:29:59.793
I'm not doing that stuff anymore.

01:30:01.340 --> 01:30:03.467
If that's true, I'm happy for you.

01:30:04.954 --> 01:30:08.319
And I know your intentions
may have not been so bad

01:30:08.320 --> 01:30:10.649
but I,

01:30:10.650 --> 01:30:13.500
just don't think I can go on
like you never did all that.

01:30:15.377 --> 01:30:16.973
It's just not something I can do.

01:30:23.066 --> 01:30:23.899
Wait here.

01:30:30.750 --> 01:30:34.003
You can have this back.
I don't want it.

01:30:39.750 --> 01:30:42.900
Actually, I will take it.

01:30:51.110 --> 01:30:52.617
Thank you for asking me out.

01:30:54.710 --> 01:30:56.593
I think you're gonna be a great father.

01:30:57.870 --> 01:30:58.703
Thanks.

01:31:01.267 --> 01:31:02.417
You should join a club.

01:31:05.340 --> 01:31:06.173
Bye Joseph.

01:31:10.810 --> 01:31:11.643
Bye Gwen.

01:31:39.428 --> 01:31:41.209
Hey!
Hey!

01:31:41.210 --> 01:31:42.819
You shaved your beard?
Yeah.

01:31:42.820 --> 01:31:45.022
Thought I'd try something a bit different.

01:31:45.023 --> 01:31:45.946
Nuh-uh.
No?

01:31:45.947 --> 01:31:47.230
No.
You don't like it?

01:31:47.231 --> 01:31:48.606
No.
You don't like it.

01:31:48.607 --> 01:31:49.712
Nah.

01:31:50.547 --> 01:31:52.359
I supposed I could try to grow it back.

01:31:52.360 --> 01:31:53.589
Good plan.

01:31:53.590 --> 01:31:54.929
So did you get your certificate?

01:31:54.930 --> 01:31:57.942
Sure did, I'm now fully
qualified to push wheelchairs

01:31:57.943 --> 01:32:00.162
and help old ladies change.

01:32:00.163 --> 01:32:02.219
Well I'm sorry I missed the ceremony.

01:32:02.220 --> 01:32:03.769
Oh you mean the one I held for myself

01:32:03.770 --> 01:32:06.349
while I waiting for them to
print out my certificate?

01:32:06.350 --> 01:32:07.769
But I got you a little something

01:32:07.770 --> 01:32:09.672
to make it feel more officious.

01:32:09.673 --> 01:32:11.229
Oh, what?

01:32:11.230 --> 01:32:13.793
It's a graduation hat, thingy.

01:32:14.658 --> 01:32:15.491
Ah-ha!

01:32:18.608 --> 01:32:19.639
Wait.

01:32:19.640 --> 01:32:20.902
Eh?
Yeah.

01:32:20.903 --> 01:32:23.714
I feel like I'm at Oxford.
You look like it.

01:32:24.830 --> 01:32:26.783
We need to get a
picture of this, come on.

01:32:32.483 --> 01:32:33.570
Make sure you get the hat.
Okay.

01:32:35.099 --> 01:32:36.459
You know what...
I'm not tall enough.

01:32:36.460 --> 01:32:38.879
Ah, just reach, stretch.
Okay.

01:32:38.880 --> 01:32:40.459
Yes!
I'm gonna wear this hat

01:32:40.460 --> 01:32:41.789
the rest of my life.
Yes.

01:32:41.790 --> 01:32:43.947
It's gonna be like
my just every day hat.

